description: Screenshots https://boltimg.com/image/GgQCI -W4F Releasing TV since 2002- Proudly Presents Wheel.Of.Fortune.S36E38.Home.Sweet.Home.3.HDTV.x264-W4F RELEASE iNFO Release Date 2018.10.31 EPiSODE iNFO W4F GROUP NEWS W4F is one of the oldest TV scene groups. We pride ourselves in releasing a diverse mix of television programming ranging from documentaries to scripted to reality tv. We release purely for fun. We are actively interested in finding individuals who would like to join the W4F family. We are interested in those who can capture content from the US. Potential recruits will preferably have the ability to receive digital TV broadcasts and some knowledge of digital capturing such as HDHomeRun, Ceton, Set-top box (STB) firewire output, etc. From time to time we are also interested in hearing from site owners who are interested in affiliating W4F. We are looking for private links with archives. W4F has nothing to do with torrents/p2p so don't ask about that! Email: w4f@tuta.io Greets to all W4F/CLASSiCW4F members, both past and present
